thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by jeff in MSP

author: jeff in MSP
title: jeff in MSP
text: I'm on a mostly vegan diet except for a weekly meal with wild salmon or sardines/mackerel. Vital Choice tinned fish is exceptional. I'm sure the frozen fish is equally wonderful, though I order tinned fish to avoid the extra shipping cost for perishable fish. Delicious, as virgin as possible. Love the product.
